# Hero Layout Redesign Plan

## Goal Description
Change the Hero section layout from a centered single-column stack to a two-column layout on desktop:
- **Left Column**: Title, description, and CTA buttons.
- **Right Column**: The `HeroTerminal` component.
- **Mobile**: Remain stacked (Text top, Terminal bottom).

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> This changes the visual hierarchy significantly on big screens.

